BNY Mellon Says CEO Kelly Steps Down

-- B y   V i v e k   S h a n k a r
-- 
2011-08-31T21:21:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-31/bny-mellon-says-ceo-kelly-steps-down.html
BNY Mellon said Robert P. Kelly
stepped down as chairman, chief executive officer and director
because of differences with the board in the approach to
managing the company.  Gerald L. Hassell was named chairman and CEO.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vivek Shankar at 
 vshankar3@bloomberg.net  